rComments: Great professor, he is very chill and laid back. He is easy to reach and helpful during office hours. The lectures are straight forward and the textbook is more for reference purposes. There isn't a lot of work to be completed in the class. The midterm and exams are based on the lecture notes and in class discussions.

His slides are made by the textbook company. All you need to do is read the text, he will only recapitulate it in lecture. Useless, useless prof. Incredibly condescending to students who seek individual consultation. He really don't seem interested in teaching at the undergraduate level. Skip this class if you can.
Can't teach at all. Makes mistakes continuously. Students have to often correct him. and His exams are VERY hard.
Extremely mundane, but lectures only what you have to know for tests
Not interesting, but clear, way better compare to parkerson
